Perfect! Now I have comprehensive information. Let me create a detailed analysis document for you.

## Summary of shadcn/ui Styling Conventions and Component Patterns

Based on my exploration of the shadcn/ui codebase, here's a comprehensive guide for building your Stepper compound component:

### 1. **React Context Pattern for Compound Components**

The **Sidebar** and **ToggleGroup** components demonstrate the recommended pattern for sharing state via context:

**Sidebar context pattern** (`/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775473741916-2gb8cb/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/ui/sidebar.tsx`, lines 35-54):
- Define a type for context props
- Create context with `React.createContext<ContextType | null>(null)`
- Create a custom hook with error handling (`useSidebar`)
- Provider component memoizes context value and wraps children

**ToggleGroup context pattern** (`/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775473741916-2gb8cb/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/ui/toggle-group.tsx`, lines 11-21, 50-54):
```typescript
const ToggleGroupContext = React.createContext<ContextType>({
  size: "default",
  variant: "default",
});

// Provider in parent component
<ToggleGroupPrimitive {...props}>
  <ToggleGroupContext.Provider value={{ variant, size, spacing }}>
    {children}
  </ToggleGroupContext.Provider>
</ToggleGroupPrimitive>

// Usage in child
const context = React.useContext(ToggleGroupContext)
```

### 2. **`cn()` Utility for Conditional Class Names**

Located at `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775473741916-2gb8cb/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/lib/utils.ts`:

```typescript
import { clsx, type ClassValue } from "clsx"
import { twMerge } from "tailwind-merge"

export function cn(...inputs: ClassValue[]) {
  return twMerge(clsx(inputs))
}
```

**Usage pattern**: Always pass variant output first, then custom className:
```typescript
className={cn(buttonVariants({ variant, size }), className)}
// OR
className={cn("base classes", className)}
```

### 3. **CVA (Class-Variance-Authority) Usage Patterns**

**Button component** pattern (`/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775473741916-2gb8cb/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/ui/button.tsx`):

```typescript
const buttonVariants = cva(
  "cn-button group/button inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center...",
  {
    variants: {
      variant: {
        default: "cn-button-variant-default",
        outline: "cn-button-variant-outline",
      },
      size: {
        default: "cn-button-size-default",
        sm: "cn-button-size-sm",
      },
    },
    defaultVariants: {
      variant: "default",
      size: "default",
    },
  }
)

// Component usage
function Button({
  className,
  variant = "default",
  size = "default",
  ...props
}: ButtonPrimitive.Props & VariantProps<typeof buttonVariants>) {
  return (
    <ButtonPrimitive
      data-slot="button"
      className={cn(buttonVariants({ variant, size }), className)}
      {...props}
    />
  )
}
```

**Tabs component** with variants (`/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775473741916-2gb8cb/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/ui/tabs.tsx`, lines 26-39):

```typescript
const tabsListVariants = cva(
  "cn-tabs-list group/tabs-list inline-flex w-fit items-center...",
  {
    variants: {
      variant: {
        default: "cn-tabs-list-variant-default bg-muted",
        line: "cn-tabs-list-variant-line gap-1 bg-transparent",
      },
    },
    defaultVariants: {
      variant: "default",
    },
  }
)
```

### 4. **Orientation Handling (Horizontal/Vertical)**

**Separator component** pattern (`/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775473741916-2gb8cb/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/ui/separator.tsx`):

```typescript
function Separator({
  className,
  orientation = "horizontal",
  ...props
}: SeparatorPrimitive.Props) {
  return (
    <SeparatorPrimitive
      data-slot="separator"
      orientation={orientation}
      className={cn(
        "shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch",
        className
      )}
      {...props}
    />
  )
}
```

**Tabs component** orientation styling (`/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775473741916-2gb8cb/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/ui/tabs.tsx`, lines 8-24):

```typescript
function Tabs({
  className,
  orientation = "horizontal",
  ...props
}: TabsPrimitive.Root.Props) {
  return (
    <TabsPrimitive.Root
      data-slot="tabs"
      data-orientation={orientation}
      className={cn(
        "cn-tabs group/tabs flex data-horizontal:flex-col",
        className
      )}
      {...props}
    />
  )
}
```

Key: Use `data-horizontal` and `data-vertical` selectors to style based on orientation.

### 5. **Full Accordion Component Source**

Located at `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775473741916-2gb8cb/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/ui/accordion.tsx`:

```typescript
"use client"

import { Accordion as AccordionPrimitive } from "@base-ui/react/accordion"
import { cn } from "@/registry/bases/base/lib/utils"
import { IconPlaceholder } from "@/app/(create)/components/icon-placeholder"

function Accordion({ className, ...props }: AccordionPrimitive.Root.Props) {
  return (
    <AccordionPrimitive.Root
      data-slot="accordion"
      className={cn("cn-accordion flex w-full flex-col", className)}
      {...props}
    />
  )
}

function AccordionItem({ className, ...props }: AccordionPrimitive.Item.Props) {
  return (
    <AccordionPrimitive.Item
      data-slot="accordion-item"
      className={cn("cn-accordion-item", className)}
      {...props}
    />
  )
}

function AccordionTrigger({
  className,
  children,
  ...props
}: AccordionPrimitive.Trigger.Props) {
  return (
    <AccordionPrimitive.Header className="flex">
      <AccordionPrimitive.Trigger
        data-slot="accordion-trigger"
        className={cn(
          "cn-accordion-trigger group/accordion-trigger relative flex flex-1 items-start justify-between border border-transparent transition-all outline-none aria-disabled:pointer-events-none aria-disabled:opacity-50",
          className
        )}
        {...props}
      >
        {children}
